# S.O.U.L

(Social Observation of Unconcious Life)

## Potentisal file structure

```python
soul/
├── main.py           # Simulation loop
├── person.py         # Person class and mood logic
├── world.py          # World, social environment
├── event.py          # Event generation logic
├── utils.py          # Helper functions
├── log.py (optional) # Logging / save / load

```

## Ideas
- **Activities**: People have different effects when they do an activity : for example person A will gain between 0 and 10 happiness when they go to the cinema, while person B will gain between 0 and 5 happiness.
